Dear [Customer's Name],

I hope this message finds you well. I am reaching out to you regarding your recent inquiry. We have completed our investigation into your claim and would like to discuss the results with you. Additionally, we have some planned adjustments that we believe will be beneficial for you.

Please let us know a convenient time for you to discuss this matter further. We value your business and are committed to providing you with the highest level of service.

Best Regards,
[Your Name]
